
WICHTIG: 	Diese Programm hat KEINEN offiziellen Linux support! 
			Einige features wie z.B die Musik funktionieren nicht auf Linux.


Controls

ESC 		- 	Schließt Spiel
ENTER 		-	Gleiche Funktion wie A-Button
BACKSPACE 	-	Gleiche Funktion wie B-Button
ARROW-KEYS	-	Gleiche Funktion wie Steuerkreuz

A-BUTTON			-	Bestätigen/Auswählen
B-BUTTON			-	Zurück
STEUERKREUTZ-DOWN	-	Down/Button beneath
STEUERKREUTZ-UP		-	Up/Button above
STEUERKREUTZ-RIGHT	-	Bestätigen/Auswählen
STEUERKREUTZ-LEFT	-	Zurück



Story:

You open your eyes and realize that you are in a unicolored room.
Suddenly a voice starts to speak. It seems to come from everywhere. 
It says: "You, last survivor of humanity! Find the Key of a thousand Snakes and prove yourself worthy."
You look around in your room and realize that it has no doors. 
So you start to go near the wall right infront of you and suddenly the roomcolor has changed! 
You must have been teleported into the next room. But without a door where do you use the key?
Well, you better start walking around searching with every of your five senses. 

